  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "The selected set of 28 papers for this SLR is available in Appendix A.",
    "Quality assessmentWe have used the five-question criteria proposed by Liu et al. [29] to evaluate the quality of our selected studies.",
    "These questions evaluate the study's empirical or non-empirical nature, limitations and future work description, findings and contributions clarity, research design suitability, and clarity.",
    "Every question was rated from 0 to 1, where 0 meant \"no,\" 0.5 meant \"partially,\" and 1 meant \"yes.\"",
    "The papers were categorized as Good if the score was between 3 and 4, Fair if it was between 2 and 3, and Poor if it was between 0 and 2."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Quality assessmentWe have used the five-question criteria proposed by Liu et al. [29] to evaluate the quality of our selected studies."
  ]
}